 Parameter (copy) (copy)_1255096945751834626] IN (&quot;CTR&quot;,&quot;Web CVR&quot;,&quot;Platform CVR&quot;) THEN&#13;&#10;    STR(ROUND(ABS([KPI 2-1 Plan Difference (copy 3)_1793840067788357639]), 2)) + &quot;%&quot;&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;// Special case preserved exactly as provided (uses [KPI 8], not vs field)&#13;&#10;ELSEIF [Parameters].[K2-2 Active Metric Parameter (copy) (copy)_1255096945751834626] IN (&quot;% Total Web Revenue&quot;) THEN&#13;&#10;    STR(ROUND(([KPI2-2 This Year (copy)_1255096945753911303]) * 100, 2)) + &quot;%&quot;&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;END"/>
