              <calculation class="tableau" formula="(([KPI1-1 Previous period (copy)_2409144348492107778])-([KPI1-1 Previous period (copy 2)_2409144348489957377]))/[KPI1-1 Previous period (copy 2)_2409144348489957377]"/>
